tial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">灵性　　每一个时节，有每一个时节的景象　　小楼一夜听<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/fengyu/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">风雨，深巷明朝卖<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/xinghua/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">杏花　　暮春三月，<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/jiangnan/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">江南草长，<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/zahuashengshu/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">杂花生树，群莺乱飞　　林断山明竹隐墙，乱蝉衰草小<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/chitang/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">池塘　　而今识尽愁<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/ziwei/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">滋味，却道天凉好个秋　　<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/zhuanti/qingkong/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">晴空一鹤排云上，便引诗情到碧霄　　花雪随风不厌看，更多还肯失林峦　　<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/fangsong/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">放松身体，放飞<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/xinqingsuibi/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">心情，带着<a href="http://www.wenzhangba.com/huati/shiqinghuayi/" class="innerlink" target="_blank" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); text-decoration-line: none;">诗情画意，触碰各种时节景象","../image/recommend/n1.jpg")
